WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.360
[Characters, behaviors, places,
organizations, and events shown in the series

00:00:02.400 --> 00:00:04.800
are entirely fictional,
are solely for entertainment purposes,

00:00:04.840 --> 00:00:07.820
with no intention to instruct
or promote any kind of behavior;

00:00:07.860 --> 00:00:10.040
viewer discretion is advised]

00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:12.840
Knowing about my past
probably won't do me any good.

00:00:16.960 --> 00:00:19.880
So I contacted Bew,
the owner of this song.

00:00:19.920 --> 00:00:23.280
She's never sung this song to anyone,
except her family members.

00:00:23.600 --> 00:00:25.200
I can't tell you anything else.

00:00:25.240 --> 00:00:27.000
This is already putting us at a lot of risk!

00:00:27.280 --> 00:00:28.480
Just trust me for once.

00:00:28.520 --> 00:00:31.440
Don't go meet anyone!

00:00:31.560 --> 00:00:33.720
Bew Rattanawee.

00:00:45.340 --> 00:00:47.840
This is Bew's Kingdom,

00:00:48.840 --> 00:00:50.320
her studio.

00:03:11.600 --> 00:03:13.120
- Hi.
- Hello.

00:03:13.160 --> 00:03:15.040
I'm here to see Ms. Bew.

00:03:15.080 --> 00:03:16.240
Oh, right.

00:03:22.590 --> 00:03:23.860
So...

00:03:25.329 --> 00:03:26.570
Is she here?

00:03:27.440 --> 00:03:28.720
Did you make an appointment to see her?

00:03:29.800 --> 00:03:30.960
Right...

00:03:31.500 --> 00:03:32.680
I didn't.

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:34.880
I called earlier,

00:03:34.920 --> 00:03:36.520
but no one picked up.

00:03:37.280 --> 00:03:39.040
Isn't she here?

00:03:39.079 --> 00:03:40.120
She is,

00:03:40.160 --> 00:03:42.760
- but...
- Bew, your ride is here.

00:04:00.760 --> 00:04:01.680
I'll leave it to you.

00:04:01.720 --> 00:04:02.560
Ms. Bew...

00:04:03.400 --> 00:04:05.880
Hello, my name is Jane.

00:04:06.140 --> 00:04:10.020
I'd like to discuss something with you.

00:04:10.200 --> 00:04:11.880
I'll call you later.
I'm going to miss my flight.

00:04:26.240 --> 00:04:27.320
My apologies,

00:04:27.360 --> 00:04:29.360
but Bew has a flight to catch today.

00:04:29.880 --> 00:04:31.160
Is she traveling abroad?

00:04:31.200 --> 00:04:33.600
Is there any way
I could get in touch with her?

00:04:33.640 --> 00:04:36.960
I really need to speak with her.

00:04:37.000 --> 00:04:38.920
This is going to be hard.

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:41.120
She's going out of town
for a meditation retreat,

00:04:41.159 --> 00:04:43.720
so she'll turn off her phone
and be out of touch for about a week.

00:04:43.920 --> 00:04:46.720
I'm afraid you'll have to wait
until after that.

00:04:52.580 --> 00:04:53.860
Gosh.

00:05:05.060 --> 00:05:07.280
Bew is such a weird person.

00:05:07.320 --> 00:05:09.760
How could someone
be off their phone for that long?

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:11.840
If that were me,

00:05:12.080 --> 00:05:13.480
I'd totally freak out.

00:05:18.440 --> 00:05:19.240
Right?

00:05:23.840 --> 00:05:25.520
Speaking of that,

00:05:25.560 --> 00:05:28.160
according to the theory,
she's already our 6th person,

00:05:28.720 --> 00:05:31.080
so she should be someone
who knows you personally.

00:05:32.280 --> 00:05:34.720
But you met her in person,

00:05:35.200 --> 00:05:36.600
and you still don't remember anything?

00:05:40.140 --> 00:05:40.960
Whoa!

00:05:42.850 --> 00:05:43.720
Z!

00:05:44.760 --> 00:05:45.560
What?

00:05:46.600 --> 00:05:47.409
Hey!

00:06:11.860 --> 00:06:12.860
What happened?

00:06:13.260 --> 00:06:16.000
Why did you suddenly pass out?

00:06:17.640 --> 00:06:18.840
My head was hurting.

00:06:23.900 --> 00:06:26.080
How can your head hurt

00:06:26.120 --> 00:06:28.480
if angels don't even sleep?

00:06:30.660 --> 00:06:31.880
I have no idea.

00:06:32.580 --> 00:06:34.240
I've never been like this before.

00:07:02.880 --> 00:07:03.960
How is it?

00:07:04.120 --> 00:07:05.160
Do you feel better?

00:07:10.380 --> 00:07:11.380
I do.

00:07:13.320 --> 00:07:14.840
Why are you so good
at giving massages?

00:07:16.440 --> 00:07:17.440
I am?

00:07:18.440 --> 00:07:20.800
I've never done this to anyone, though.

00:07:40.120 --> 00:07:43.800
Why did you suddenly get
those symptoms?

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:48.200
I don't know.

00:07:50.440 --> 00:07:52.400
My head just started hurting

00:07:52.840 --> 00:07:54.720
when we were at Bew's studio.

00:07:56.840 --> 00:07:58.880
Ever since we were at the studio?

00:08:10.640 --> 00:08:12.600
See? I knew it.

00:08:13.020 --> 00:08:16.040
You and Bew probably knew each other.

00:08:23.800 --> 00:08:25.080
I don't know...

00:08:26.200 --> 00:08:28.400
But besides the headache,

00:08:29.000 --> 00:08:30.840
I felt something strange, too.

00:08:31.640 --> 00:08:32.840
How strange was it?

00:08:35.880 --> 00:08:37.760
I felt empty,

00:08:39.600 --> 00:08:41.360
but it wasn't exactly sad.

00:08:48.920 --> 00:08:50.240
It's hurting again.

00:09:00.760 --> 00:09:01.540
Come here.

00:09:10.400 --> 00:09:11.400
Lie down here.

00:09:12.940 --> 00:09:13.840
Come on.

00:09:15.700 --> 00:09:16.700
Easy.

00:09:43.880 --> 00:09:44.880
Jane...

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:47.400
What are you doing?

00:09:57.160 --> 00:10:00.040
In Japan, this is how they check for fever.

00:10:06.040 --> 00:10:08.840
But you don't have a fever.

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:14.160
So...

00:10:17.220 --> 00:10:18.700
Is your head still hurting?

00:10:22.260 --> 00:10:23.440
It's fine now.

00:10:25.940 --> 00:10:27.520
It's like I never had one.

00:10:52.320 --> 00:10:53.560
She had a headache?

00:10:56.400 --> 00:10:58.760
She seems fine now.

00:10:59.100 --> 00:11:00.100
Well...

00:11:01.580 --> 00:11:03.040
I helped her

00:11:03.400 --> 00:11:04.560
before we came here.

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:06.360
How so?

00:11:10.480 --> 00:11:11.520
Staring into her eyes.

00:11:11.560 --> 00:11:12.560
Staring into her eyes?

00:11:17.080 --> 00:11:18.920
Whenever I look into her eyes,

00:11:19.340 --> 00:11:21.020
her whole world just stops.

00:11:23.040 --> 00:11:24.840
Girl!

00:11:25.520 --> 00:11:27.760
The audacity.
Where did you get that confidence from?

00:11:27.800 --> 00:11:30.240
What? I'm telling you the truth.

00:11:30.280 --> 00:11:31.480
Alright, prove it.

00:11:31.640 --> 00:11:34.800
Tell us how that helped her.

00:11:35.700 --> 00:11:38.200
Her body works in a really bizarre way.

00:11:38.240 --> 00:11:40.120
She can't sleep

00:11:40.160 --> 00:11:42.280
or take any medicine.

00:11:42.560 --> 00:11:44.000
We didn't even know
how to deal with her headache.

00:11:45.220 --> 00:11:46.400
But I...

00:11:47.140 --> 00:11:49.440
stumbled upon something...

00:11:52.680 --> 00:11:53.440
What is it?

00:11:55.940 --> 00:11:56.840
Well...

00:11:58.320 --> 00:12:01.000
The more I make her heart race,

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:04.680
the less her head hurts.

00:12:09.380 --> 00:12:12.880
So when you said "make her heart race,"

00:12:13.980 --> 00:12:15.200
did you actually mean your heart?

00:12:17.760 --> 00:12:18.640
No!

00:12:18.960 --> 00:12:22.040
So are you saying that she's into you?

00:12:25.550 --> 00:12:26.400
Right?

00:12:27.540 --> 00:12:28.720
I don't know!

00:12:28.920 --> 00:12:30.320
Is it just all in your head?

00:12:33.680 --> 00:12:37.000
But I really tried it out at home.

00:12:38.560 --> 00:12:41.280
Guys, it's not like that!

00:12:42.640 --> 00:12:43.640
Alright, alright...

00:12:44.060 --> 00:12:45.400
Look how much she's grown up.

00:12:46.400 --> 00:12:48.520
See? If she's even
a little far away from me,

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:50.000
she gets a headache.

00:12:50.660 --> 00:12:52.040
I'll show you.

00:12:58.400 --> 00:12:59.680
Girl, come here.

00:12:59.720 --> 00:13:00.640
Quick!

00:13:00.680 --> 00:13:01.880
- Come here.
- Girl, come quick.

00:13:12.880 --> 00:13:13.710
Goodness!

00:13:19.120 --> 00:13:20.400
Jane, what are you doing?

00:13:21.000 --> 00:13:22.160
There are people around.

00:13:23.840 --> 00:13:25.040
I just want to hug you.

00:13:35.880 --> 00:13:36.680
Gosh!

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:46.520
She's really into you.

00:13:48.400 --> 00:13:50.720
It's nice of you to help
with her headache,

00:13:50.760 --> 00:13:52.120
but what you've done

00:13:52.560 --> 00:13:54.480
is just toying with her feelings.

00:13:54.520 --> 00:13:57.840
If I don't do that,

00:13:57.880 --> 00:14:00.280
do you expect her
to stay in pain all day?

00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:02.720
What if her headache goes away?

00:14:05.700 --> 00:14:07.320
You're messing with her head.

00:14:09.760 --> 00:14:11.480
I'm not.

00:14:12.640 --> 00:14:14.040
Actually...

00:14:14.360 --> 00:14:16.080
I feel the same way she does.

00:14:16.120 --> 00:14:17.080
- Huh?!
- What?!

00:14:21.200 --> 00:14:22.200
Well...

00:14:24.000 --> 00:14:25.480
I really like her.

00:14:26.560 --> 00:14:29.280
But you know all too well
that she won't be around forever.

00:14:29.320 --> 00:14:30.360
One day, she'll have to go.

00:14:30.400 --> 00:14:31.960
What are you planning to do then?

00:14:34.120 --> 00:14:35.760
No clue.

00:14:36.680 --> 00:14:38.360
But I already fell for her.

00:14:38.830 --> 00:14:39.960
We have a big problem.

00:14:40.640 --> 00:14:42.160
This could get messy.

00:15:10.400 --> 00:15:13.080
How can I take care of you
while I'm asleep?

00:15:18.040 --> 00:15:19.480
It's fine, Jane.

00:15:23.440 --> 00:15:24.760
I'm so sorry.

00:15:27.320 --> 00:15:28.560
Why would you be?

00:15:28.800 --> 00:15:30.120
It's not your fault.

00:15:30.940 --> 00:15:32.200
You're just sick.

00:15:56.080 --> 00:15:57.280
What are you doing?

00:15:57.920 --> 00:16:01.640
Tonight, just hold me this way.

00:16:02.880 --> 00:16:04.000
Don't you let go.

00:16:07.000 --> 00:16:08.120
But...

00:16:09.080 --> 00:16:10.400
No buts.

00:16:11.180 --> 00:16:13.000
This is an order.

00:16:30.360 --> 00:16:32.120
If I hadn't found out on my own,

00:16:32.640 --> 00:16:34.480
when were you planning to tell me?

00:16:35.040 --> 00:16:37.000
I...

00:16:37.040 --> 00:16:38.760
Or were you not planning
to tell me at all?

00:16:39.980 --> 00:16:41.360
I'm very sorry, Miss Kaew-Ta.

00:16:41.400 --> 00:16:42.680
I was just...

00:16:59.000 --> 00:17:01.000
Make yourself presentable.

00:17:01.630 --> 00:17:03.150
You're my assistant, after all.

00:17:04.240 --> 00:17:07.119
Don't let anyone say
that I trained you poorly.

00:17:14.000 --> 00:17:15.560
I'll tell Z

00:17:15.599 --> 00:17:16.800
not to do this again.

00:17:16.839 --> 00:17:17.720
No need.

00:17:18.960 --> 00:17:20.319
I'll handle it this time.

00:17:34.880 --> 00:17:38.280
It's good to take a nice walk
once in a while.

00:17:43.960 --> 00:17:46.040
What? What's going on?

00:17:46.280 --> 00:17:47.280
Does your head hurt?

00:17:47.680 --> 00:17:51.360
When I think about Bew,
it just starts hurting.

00:18:12.600 --> 00:18:13.600
No more thinking
about someone else.

00:18:13.880 --> 00:18:16.400
Since you're with me today,

00:18:16.440 --> 00:18:17.880
I should be the only one on your mind.

00:18:23.740 --> 00:18:24.560
Let's go.

00:18:34.520 --> 00:18:37.000
The weather
is so nice today, don't you think?

00:18:39.270 --> 00:18:40.310
This looks so pretty.

00:18:40.700 --> 00:18:41.700
Let's take some photos.

00:18:43.720 --> 00:18:45.040
Three, two, one...

00:18:47.720 --> 00:18:49.360
The catch is that
we need to strike the same pose.

00:18:49.400 --> 00:18:50.560
Three, two, one.

00:18:52.200 --> 00:18:53.600
These are not the same poses!

00:18:55.560 --> 00:18:56.680
- Yay!
- Yay!

00:19:05.200 --> 00:19:06.680
These came out pretty good.

00:19:12.200 --> 00:19:13.360
Jane, look.

00:19:13.840 --> 00:19:14.640
What?

00:19:14.960 --> 00:19:16.040
My outfit.

00:19:16.080 --> 00:19:19.480
Why am I not in costume?

00:19:23.200 --> 00:19:25.080
Wait, you're right.

00:19:29.580 --> 00:19:30.640
Maybe those in charge
of your wardrobe forgot.

00:19:30.680 --> 00:19:32.880
That's wild. There's no one for that.

00:19:33.300 --> 00:19:35.040
Well, who knows?

00:19:38.040 --> 00:19:39.920
Still, I don't think that's the case.

00:19:41.840 --> 00:19:43.080
Fine, just forget it.

00:19:43.120 --> 00:19:44.960
Come on, let's get back to our walk.

00:19:45.260 --> 00:19:46.060
Let's go.

00:20:22.200 --> 00:20:23.880
Wait, what's this game?

00:20:23.920 --> 00:20:28.320
"Station: Let Your Heart Flow
with Music and Love."

00:20:32.120 --> 00:20:33.240
Interesting.

00:20:33.800 --> 00:20:36.520
"Two players will stand
at the starting point.

00:20:37.050 --> 00:20:40.080
Each of them will have
a pair of headphones and a music player

00:20:40.120 --> 00:20:41.560
playing the same song.

00:20:41.920 --> 00:20:43.760
When the song starts,

00:20:44.000 --> 00:20:47.680
they have to jump in sync
with the right notes and rhythm."

00:20:48.680 --> 00:20:50.440
Wow, that sounds like fun.

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:52.440
Isn't this for kids?

00:20:52.640 --> 00:20:54.480
Come on, we're not in our 60s!

00:20:57.760 --> 00:20:58.480
Fine.

00:21:07.520 --> 00:21:09.240
Okay, ready?

00:21:09.440 --> 00:21:10.440
- Do...
- Do...

00:21:10.680 --> 00:21:11.800
Re, mi...

00:21:12.720 --> 00:21:13.680
Do, mi...

00:21:13.720 --> 00:21:14.680
Do, mi...

00:21:15.200 --> 00:21:15.880
Re...

00:21:16.000 --> 00:21:17.120
Mi, fa,

00:21:17.280 --> 00:21:18.000
fa...

00:21:18.760 --> 00:21:19.880
Mi, re, mi...

00:21:21.360 --> 00:21:22.560
We already lost.

00:21:43.160 --> 00:21:44.080
Are you tired?

00:21:44.160 --> 00:21:45.400
Come here.

00:22:32.240 --> 00:22:34.400
I jumped so many times
that I'm soaked in sweat.

00:22:35.800 --> 00:22:37.320
Well, I'm not.

00:22:37.960 --> 00:22:40.040
That's because you can't even sweat.

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:44.240
But I did get tired...

00:22:55.970 --> 00:22:57.310
This feels very comfortable.

00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:01.320
I'm so tired...

00:23:22.720 --> 00:23:23.720
Let me have a look.

00:23:25.480 --> 00:23:26.960
Here you go.

00:23:32.360 --> 00:23:33.760
This one looks cute.

00:23:37.000 --> 00:23:38.360
You have to keep some distance.

00:23:38.690 --> 00:23:41.130
If she's not having a headache,
don't you think you should stop?

00:23:41.160 --> 00:23:43.360
You'd better not toy
with people's feelings.

00:24:25.840 --> 00:24:27.000
I got it now.

00:24:29.240 --> 00:24:30.240
What do you mean?

00:24:33.280 --> 00:24:34.760
The reason you're staying so close

00:24:36.240 --> 00:24:39.040
is to cure my headaches.

00:24:40.440 --> 00:24:41.320
What?!

00:24:43.920 --> 00:24:46.320
"You'd better not toy
with people's feelings."

00:24:48.480 --> 00:24:49.760
That was from Izzy.

00:24:53.320 --> 00:24:56.600
Hey, it's not like that at all.

00:24:58.560 --> 00:24:59.560
Just take it.

00:25:00.960 --> 00:25:01.840
What?

00:25:05.080 --> 00:25:06.080
Where are you going?

00:25:08.840 --> 00:25:10.280
Don't follow me.

00:25:10.720 --> 00:25:12.080
I want to be alone.

00:25:20.720 --> 00:25:22.360
Don't go!

00:25:50.460 --> 00:25:51.760
There you are.

00:25:52.240 --> 00:25:53.720
I've been looking everywhere for you.

00:26:07.000 --> 00:26:08.360
Your head is still hurting, right?

00:26:18.000 --> 00:26:19.120
Stop it, Jane.

00:26:20.320 --> 00:26:21.600
I realize now

00:26:22.040 --> 00:26:23.680
that what happened
between us wasn't real.

00:26:24.480 --> 00:26:25.320
Huh?

00:26:27.300 --> 00:26:28.620
Don't force it.

00:26:35.920 --> 00:26:36.920
Z!

00:27:07.240 --> 00:27:08.570
Do you wanna talk to that table?

00:27:09.000 --> 00:27:10.000
- Whoa!
- Guys!

00:27:10.180 --> 00:27:11.080
Guys!

00:27:13.840 --> 00:27:15.040
Have you seen Z?

00:27:16.000 --> 00:27:18.200
I'm right here.
How would I know?

00:27:20.360 --> 00:27:22.040
Where is she?

00:27:22.080 --> 00:27:23.920
I've been looking for her all day now.

00:27:24.520 --> 00:27:25.520
Did you fight?

00:27:26.640 --> 00:27:27.640
Or is it that...

00:27:28.320 --> 00:27:31.080
Those above have taken her back?

00:27:32.420 --> 00:27:33.880
Oh, my gosh. That's harsh.

00:27:34.000 --> 00:27:35.000
Oh, my gosh!

00:27:35.040 --> 00:27:37.880
Jeez, you're literally
just saying random things now.

00:27:38.060 --> 00:27:39.440
Get back to work!

00:27:39.480 --> 00:27:40.800
I'll take care of her.

00:27:40.840 --> 00:27:41.840
- Party pooper.
- Alright.

00:27:42.040 --> 00:27:42.960
Give me a moment, girl.

00:27:43.000 --> 00:27:44.960
Your curves are getting in my way!

00:27:45.120 --> 00:27:46.040
Get a move on!

00:27:48.820 --> 00:27:50.320
You guys fought again, didn't you?

00:27:53.140 --> 00:27:54.000
Just a little.

00:27:54.040 --> 00:27:56.480
I literally called it.

00:27:59.040 --> 00:28:00.840
What do I do?

00:28:21.360 --> 00:28:22.240
Z!

00:28:23.320 --> 00:28:24.200
Duang-Jai!

00:28:26.600 --> 00:28:27.480
You scared me!

00:28:27.510 --> 00:28:28.690
Run, Z.

00:28:29.880 --> 00:28:30.800
From what?

00:28:30.840 --> 00:28:32.640
Come on, just do as I say.
Don't be around here.

00:28:32.680 --> 00:28:34.440
Someone's coming after you.

00:28:35.760 --> 00:28:37.440
- Who?
- The warden.

00:28:37.840 --> 00:28:38.680
Huh?!

00:28:39.320 --> 00:28:40.320
Hurry up!

00:28:40.840 --> 00:28:42.680
If you get caught,
you'll be in serious trouble.

00:28:43.480 --> 00:28:44.480
From now on,

00:28:44.840 --> 00:28:47.400
use the mailbox near Tony's bar
to communicate.

00:28:48.040 --> 00:28:49.040
Duang-Jai.

00:28:53.540 --> 00:28:55.540
Stay away from where you used to go.

00:28:57.240 --> 00:28:58.240
Good luck.

00:29:05.920 --> 00:29:08.120
I've looked everywhere
and found nothing, Miss Kaew-Ta.

00:29:11.320 --> 00:29:13.040
Are you sure you haven't seen her?

00:29:13.800 --> 00:29:15.400
I...

00:29:15.780 --> 00:29:17.000
I'm sure, ma'am.

00:29:18.040 --> 00:29:19.960
But the GPS says
she's around here somewhere.

00:29:20.960 --> 00:29:23.480
Shouldn't we head back
to the office for tonight?

00:29:24.640 --> 00:29:26.640
I doubt we will find her.

00:29:27.080 --> 00:29:28.080
We have to.

00:29:30.120 --> 00:29:30.880
Follow me.

00:29:34.320 --> 00:29:35.480
Hurry!

00:29:42.600 --> 00:29:44.200
What was Duang-Jai talking about?

00:30:24.000 --> 00:30:25.680
Where does the GPS say she is?

00:30:27.120 --> 00:30:28.200
Hand me the tablet.

00:30:35.360 --> 00:30:37.680
She's left Bew's Studio.

00:30:37.960 --> 00:30:39.040
Please follow me.

00:31:14.040 --> 00:31:15.200
We're safe now.

00:31:16.400 --> 00:31:17.280
Let's go.

00:31:49.280 --> 00:31:51.480
I'm sorry for dragging you into this.

00:31:53.080 --> 00:31:54.360
Why would you be?

00:31:55.340 --> 00:31:56.940
You didn't do anything wrong.

00:32:00.020 --> 00:32:02.440
So how did you know where I was?

00:32:03.560 --> 00:32:04.560
Well...

00:32:04.840 --> 00:32:06.040
I didn't.

00:32:06.280 --> 00:32:10.120
I just guessed based on
the places we used to go.

00:32:10.560 --> 00:32:14.000
Then Bew's studio came to mind,

00:32:14.240 --> 00:32:15.320
so I decided to try my luck there.

00:32:19.440 --> 00:32:21.120
Is that pretty lady

00:32:21.880 --> 00:32:23.600
really gonna punish you?

00:32:26.080 --> 00:32:27.080
I don't know,

00:32:27.980 --> 00:32:29.520
but Duang-Jai never lies to me.

00:32:32.240 --> 00:32:34.320
But you're just doing what I want,

00:32:34.760 --> 00:32:37.120
and I'm the one
who redeemed you with my points

00:32:38.280 --> 00:32:39.880
I don't think it's foul play.

00:32:41.280 --> 00:32:42.440
That's typical of you.

00:32:43.000 --> 00:32:45.280
What? I mean it!

00:32:45.920 --> 00:32:48.000
Since there's a loophole in the rules,

00:32:48.320 --> 00:32:51.760
we've gotta make use of it, right?

00:33:03.840 --> 00:33:05.520
Why do I have so many points?

00:33:06.220 --> 00:33:08.280
I was sure I redeemed them all last time.

00:33:10.620 --> 00:33:11.920
Maybe it's because of the shio pan?

00:33:13.040 --> 00:33:15.160
Your shio pan brings people joy,

00:33:15.560 --> 00:33:16.920
so you earn more points.

00:33:31.920 --> 00:33:33.120
I have an idea.

00:33:34.520 --> 00:33:35.400
What is it?

00:33:35.880 --> 00:33:36.800
I'm not telling you.

00:33:37.680 --> 00:33:38.960
Let me see!

00:33:43.220 --> 00:33:44.360
There's nothing to see.

00:34:21.920 --> 00:34:24.600
I almost broke my neck.

00:34:30.380 --> 00:34:33.260
I thought I wasn't gonna
fall asleep tonight.

00:34:40.840 --> 00:34:42.199
I think...

00:34:44.440 --> 00:34:46.920
you should return me to the app.

00:34:48.760 --> 00:34:50.280
That way, you don't have
to go through all these troubles.

00:34:53.199 --> 00:34:55.010
You're really misunderstanding me.

00:34:56.080 --> 00:34:57.440
How am I?

00:34:58.060 --> 00:34:59.860
It's clear that you're having a hard time.

00:35:05.090 --> 00:35:06.440
I'm not.

00:35:06.480 --> 00:35:08.280
You decided that I was.

00:35:12.760 --> 00:35:14.080
Anyway,

00:35:15.040 --> 00:35:18.760
one day, I'll be sent back
to face punishment.

00:35:20.380 --> 00:35:21.560
You'd better just...

00:35:22.760 --> 00:35:24.400
return me now.

00:35:28.940 --> 00:35:30.220
No way.

00:35:32.520 --> 00:35:33.880
Not a chance.

00:35:45.500 --> 00:35:46.720
Listen.

00:35:49.520 --> 00:35:52.760
The reason I've been close to you
these past few days

00:35:54.640 --> 00:35:57.480
is not just about getting rid
of your headache.

00:35:59.600 --> 00:36:01.320
I was like that...

00:36:05.240 --> 00:36:06.720
because I genuinely wanted to be.

00:36:10.800 --> 00:36:12.320
I really like you.

00:36:21.680 --> 00:36:22.680
No,

00:36:23.240 --> 00:36:24.760
it's just sympathy.

00:36:26.440 --> 00:36:27.440
Or maybe...

00:37:41.720 --> 00:37:43.840
Do you still think...

00:37:46.080 --> 00:37:47.880
it's just sympathy?

00:38:22.080 --> 00:38:23.240
Is it morning already?

00:38:34.280 --> 00:38:35.560
What's that stare?

00:38:38.000 --> 00:38:41.240
Last night, before you came to find me,

00:38:42.680 --> 00:38:44.120
you were with Auntie Itt, right?

00:38:45.100 --> 00:38:46.480
I was.

00:38:48.900 --> 00:38:50.280
So...

00:38:52.320 --> 00:38:54.120
Were you drunk from that herbal liquor?

00:38:55.120 --> 00:38:56.680
Are you out of your mind?

00:38:56.960 --> 00:38:59.080
I went to her bar,

00:38:59.320 --> 00:39:01.880
but when I saw you weren't there,

00:39:02.040 --> 00:39:03.240
I left.

00:39:03.280 --> 00:39:05.400
I didn't drink a single drop of it.

00:39:08.720 --> 00:39:10.920
So that means you were fully conscious...

00:39:16.880 --> 00:39:17.880
Why?

00:39:20.640 --> 00:39:21.680
I'm just asking.

00:39:28.580 --> 00:39:31.680
Right... I know why.

00:39:32.920 --> 00:39:35.880
You're doubting my confession, aren't you?

00:39:39.320 --> 00:39:40.320
No.

00:39:42.160 --> 00:39:43.160
Really?

00:39:45.400 --> 00:39:46.400
Yeah.

00:39:51.200 --> 00:39:53.840
I really wasn't drunk.

00:39:54.820 --> 00:39:57.200
If you want me to say it again,

00:39:57.640 --> 00:39:58.820
I will.

00:40:10.520 --> 00:40:11.520
What are you doing?

00:40:15.840 --> 00:40:17.240
Do you want me to prove it?

00:40:25.200 --> 00:40:26.400
Back off...

00:40:26.940 --> 00:40:28.440
You haven't even brushed your teeth,

00:40:29.120 --> 00:40:30.560
and you want to kiss me?

00:40:41.260 --> 00:40:42.940
I haven't brushed my teeth
since last night.

00:41:03.680 --> 00:41:04.760
Can you help me brush my teeth?

00:41:13.000 --> 00:41:14.400
Are they clean now?

00:41:17.340 --> 00:41:18.480
I don't know.

00:41:18.760 --> 00:41:19.480
What?

00:42:17.960 --> 00:42:19.560
Now, that's kissable.

00:42:22.960 --> 00:42:23.880
You're such a goof.

00:42:24.480 --> 00:42:25.760
Don't be this hot around me.

00:42:39.840 --> 00:42:41.680
So what are we gonna do next?

00:42:42.080 --> 00:42:45.000
Will Ms. Pretty Warden
really take you in for punishment?

00:42:45.720 --> 00:42:46.720
I have no clue.

00:42:47.280 --> 00:42:48.880
That's everything
Duang-Jai has told me.

00:42:51.480 --> 00:42:52.640
From now on,

00:42:52.880 --> 00:42:55.280
use the mailbox near Tony's bar
to communicate.

00:42:56.600 --> 00:42:57.600
I got it!

00:42:59.160 --> 00:43:01.360
We're going to Tony's bar.

00:43:01.940 --> 00:43:02.760
Huh?!

00:43:03.380 --> 00:43:04.440
What for?

00:43:04.720 --> 00:43:06.720
We're already safe here.

00:43:07.260 --> 00:43:10.120
Well, Duang-Jai told me earlier

00:43:10.160 --> 00:43:11.960
that if I wanted to reach him,

00:43:12.000 --> 00:43:14.640
I had to use the mailbox near the bar.

00:43:16.480 --> 00:43:19.480
Maybe he's already sent us some letters.

00:43:20.420 --> 00:43:21.640
Wait here, then.

00:43:21.800 --> 00:43:22.800
I'll go there.

00:43:22.840 --> 00:43:23.720
No!

00:43:24.040 --> 00:43:25.160
You stay here.

00:43:25.360 --> 00:43:27.240
Why would you go out there
and put yourself at risk?

00:43:27.640 --> 00:43:28.800
I'll go.

00:43:28.960 --> 00:43:29.880
No!

00:43:29.920 --> 00:43:33.160
I was the one who pushed you
to find your identity.

00:43:33.400 --> 00:43:34.920
I'm totally at fault here!

00:43:37.400 --> 00:43:38.400
You're so stubborn!

00:43:39.380 --> 00:43:40.540
You're so stubborn!

00:43:44.680 --> 00:43:45.880
Fine...

00:43:48.600 --> 00:43:49.880
We'll both go.

00:43:50.700 --> 00:43:52.720
Fine, we'll both go.

00:44:16.160 --> 00:44:17.160
Cleared!

00:44:26.000 --> 00:44:26.920
Cleared!

00:44:40.520 --> 00:44:41.920
[From Duang-Jai]

00:44:43.320 --> 00:44:44.840
"From Duang-Jai."

00:44:52.680 --> 00:44:56.320
"Hi, Z. I hope you're safe and sound.

00:44:56.760 --> 00:44:59.320
The warden has found out

00:44:59.350 --> 00:45:01.880
about your search for your old identity.

00:45:04.240 --> 00:45:05.960
Considering your headache,

00:45:06.000 --> 00:45:09.840
I think Bew,
the person you met a few days ago,

00:45:09.860 --> 00:45:12.520
was probably someone
you knew personally."

00:45:19.240 --> 00:45:20.400
This house?

00:45:23.360 --> 00:45:24.240
Yes.

00:45:32.080 --> 00:45:32.960
Here are your visitor passes.

00:45:40.850 --> 00:45:43.760
"To tell you the truth,
the warden has been onto you for a while."

00:45:50.840 --> 00:45:52.440
Heaven's order.

00:46:19.040 --> 00:46:21.000
"If you get caught,
you'll face serious punishment

00:46:22.240 --> 00:46:23.790
because she's extremely angry.

00:46:25.790 --> 00:46:27.540
The best way to go from here
is to keep running

00:46:27.570 --> 00:46:29.750
until there's a change of warden.

00:46:31.600 --> 00:46:32.910
When that happens,

00:46:33.760 --> 00:46:35.360
the punishment might be less severe."

00:46:39.480 --> 00:46:40.480
What?!

00:46:42.360 --> 00:46:43.920
That's everything he wrote.

00:46:47.940 --> 00:46:49.320
What do I do now?

00:46:56.440 --> 00:46:57.640
Duang-Jai...

00:47:14.480 --> 00:47:15.480
I'm very sorry!

00:47:16.080 --> 00:47:17.680
Quick! Run!

00:49:06.640 --> 00:49:08.400
You're well aware
that you violated the rules, aren't you?

00:49:09.680 --> 00:49:11.880
I've wasted way too much time on this.

00:49:12.320 --> 00:49:13.320
Come with me.

00:49:13.940 --> 00:49:15.200
Where are you taking us?

00:49:15.240 --> 00:49:16.400
I'm not talking to you.

00:49:17.040 --> 00:49:18.400
That's even worse.

00:49:18.440 --> 00:49:20.360
I'm not letting you take her from me.

00:49:21.320 --> 00:49:22.880
It's my fault

00:49:22.920 --> 00:49:24.720
for letting it drag on this long.

00:49:26.160 --> 00:49:27.720
If I let this continue,

00:49:28.120 --> 00:49:29.720
not only will there be
severe punishment,

00:49:30.160 --> 00:49:32.760
but the remaining month of the mission
could also be shortened

00:49:33.360 --> 00:49:35.240
depending on
how serious the offense is.

00:50:36.840 --> 00:50:37.960
What does that mean?

00:50:38.320 --> 00:50:39.320
Huh?!

00:50:39.480 --> 00:50:40.880
I'd like to warn you.

00:50:41.840 --> 00:50:43.920
If there's something you want to do,
just go for it,

00:50:44.160 --> 00:50:46.400
so you won't regret it.

00:50:46.760 --> 00:50:51.160
I don't know
how much time we have left,

00:50:52.820 --> 00:50:54.400
but right at this moment,

00:50:55.000 --> 00:50:56.320
we're officially together.

00:50:56.520 --> 00:50:58.320
Whatever you say goes.

00:50:58.440 --> 00:51:00.520
What do couples

00:51:01.160 --> 00:51:02.360
usually do?